-------------------------------------
deathrun_tp_percolate_oreo
-------------------------------------
This is a deathrun map. 

The objective is for the CTs to get to the end of the map without dying from the traps which are operated by the Ts. When you win you get a shotgun to blow off the Ts' heads. The glass starts breaking (I think after 30 or 40 seconds), you must run fast or die.
-------------------------------------
Spawns
CT = 35 spawns (most deathrun servers are 18 slots with 3 Ts and the rest CT)
T = 3 spawns
-------------------------------------
